title spa new_note


note over browser:
browser has rendered notes 
to display on application start
end note 


note over browser:
User enters a note "Hello Hello" 
into the text input box, and press Save -button. 
Spa.js updates browsers internal notes list and redraws
display, after which sends HTTP POST request to server
end note
browser->server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
server-->browser: HTTP 201 response:{"message":"note created"}
note over browser:
event handler in browser spa.js after receiving 201
writes {"message":"note created"} to console
end note
